display_long_description:
Join our Discord 👉 https://discord.gg/7HPraHzTtY

 **New update – a lot of fun & cool transformations!** 

Get ready for the ultimate VR festival experience with thrilling rides, funfair games, and endless ways to customize your look. We’re turning up the fun with new outfits, magical snacks, and a mysterious new food ability system that changes the way you play!
[media]

**What’s New in the Update?**

🌸 Edible Flowers – Why gift flowers when you can eat them? Tasty & romantic!
[media]

👼 New Outfits – Dress as an angel or devil, or rock a new t-shirt!
[media]

🍽️ Food Abilities – Eat certain foods and unlock crazy transformations! Grow huge, shrink tiny, speed up, or turn into something unexpected! 🤯 
[media]

[media]

[media]

**Why You’ll Love the Game**

🎯 Classic Fairground Games – Shooting range, can toss & more!

🎢 Thrilling Rides – Roller coasters, motion-packed attractions & bumper cars!

👕 Avatar Customization – Dress in Bavarian or trendy outfits!

🎤 Social & Multiplayer Fun – Dance, chat & play together!

🎮 Mini-Games & Challenges – Rock-Paper-Scissors, rhythm games & leaderboards!

[media]

Jump in now and explore all the surprises🎉
